// Chosen Moves
.sheet-OPBHead.sheet-MinorHead.sheet-space-above(data-i18n='the-chosen') The Chosen
.sheet-Chosen
	i
		span(data-i18n='2-fixed-moves') You get these two
	| :
.sheet-Chosen.sheet-OPB
	input.sheet-triggerbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-MovesUnused', value='1', checked='')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_FixedMoves-Chosen1')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='chosen-fixed1')
				b Destiny&apos;s Plaything
				| : 
				i At the beginning of each mystery,
				|  roll +Weird 
				i to see what is revealed about your immediate future
				| . On a 10+, the Keeper will reveal a useful detail about the coming mystery. On a 7-9, you get a vague hint about it. On a miss, something bad is going to happen to you.
			|  
			button.sheet-2d6-button(type='roll', value="&{template:motw-dieroll} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{title=Destiny's Plaything}} {{Roll=[[2d6+?{Destiny's Plaything with|Weird (Default),@{Weird}|Charm,@{Charm}|Cool,@{Cool}|Sharp,@{Sharp}|Tough,@{Tough}|Weird,@{Weird}}+?{+/- forward?|0}]]}}", name='roll_dplay')
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-fixed1}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_FixedMoves-Chosen2')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			input.sheet-SettingCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_Game-World', value='0')
			span.sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches
				span(data-i18n='chosen-fixed2')
					b I&apos;m Here for a Reason
					| : There&apos;s something you are destined to do. Work out the details with the Keeper, based on your fate. You cannot die until it comes to pass. 
					i If you die in play
					| , then you must spend a 
					i Luck
					|  point. You will then, somehow, recover or be returned to life. Once your task is done, (or you use up all your 
					i Luck
					| ), all bets are off.
				button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-fixed2}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
			span.sheet-Setting-Bone
				+translate('<b>I’m Here for a Reason</b>: There’s something you are destined to do. Work out the details with the Keeper, based on your fate. You cannot die until it comes to pass. <i>If you die in play,</i> then you must spend a <i>Favour</i> point. You will then, somehow, recover or be returned to life. Once your task is done (or you use up all your <i>Favour</i>), all bets are off.')
				button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=<b>I’m Here for a Reason</b>: There’s something you are destined to do. Work out the details with the Keeper, based on your fate. You cannot die until it comes to pass. <i>If you die in play,</i> then you must spend a <i>Favour</i> point. You will then, somehow, recover or be returned to life. Once your task is done (or you use up all your <i>Favour</i>), all bets are off.}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')

// .sheet-Chosen .sheet-OPB
.sheet-Chosen
	i
		span(data-i18n='1-move') Then pick one of these
	| :
.sheet-Chosen.sheet-OPB
	input.sheet-triggerbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-MovesUnused', value='1', checked='')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Chosen1')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='chosen-move1')
				b The Big Entrance
				| : 
				i When you make a showy entrance into a dangerous situation
				| , roll +Cool. On a 10+, everyone stops to watch and listen until you finish your opening speech. On a 7-9, you pick one person or monster to stop, watch and listen until you finish talking. On a miss, you&apos;re marked as the biggest threat by all enemies who are present.
			button.sheet-2d6-button(type='roll', value='&{template:motw-dieroll} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{title=The Big Entrance}} {{Roll=[[2d6+?{The Big Entrance with|Cool (Default),@{Cool}|Charm,@{Charm}|Cool,@{Cool}|Sharp,@{Sharp}|Tough,@{Tough}|Weird,@{Weird}}+?{+/- forward?|0}]]}}', name='roll_bigentrance')
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-move1}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Chosen2')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='chosen-move2')
				b Devastating
				| : 
				i When you inflict harm
				| , you may inflict +1 harm.
			|  
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-move2}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Chosen3')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='chosen-move3')
				b Dutiful
				| : When your fate rears its ugly head, and 
				i you act in accordance with any of your fate tags
				|  (either heroic or doom), then mark experience. If it&apos;s a heroic tag, take +1 forward.
			|  
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-move3}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Chosen4')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='chosen-move4')
				b Invincible
				| : You always count as having 2 armour. This doesn&apos;t stack with other protection.
			|  
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-move4}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Chosen5')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			input.sheet-SettingCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_Game-World', value='0')
			span.sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches
				span(data-i18n='chosen-move5')
					b Resilience
					| : You heal faster than normal people. Any time your harm gets healed, heal 1 extra point. Additionally, your wounds count as 1 harm less for the purpose of the Keeper&apos;s harm moves.
				|  
			span.sheet-Setting-Bone
				+translate('<b>Resilience</b>: You heal faster than normal people. You always recover +1-harm when you make the <i>daily endure harm</i> move. Additionally, your wounds count as 1-harm less for the purpose of the Keeper’s harm moves.')
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=chosen-move5}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
